  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Ellicott's Commentary for English Readers",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(7-13) God’s revelation to Solomon by night. (Comp. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1Kings 3:5-15",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".)",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(7) In that night did God appear unto Solomon.—Kings, “In Gibeon did Jehovah appear unto Solomon in a dream of the night.” Our text fixes the night as that which followed the sacrifices; the parallel passage explicitly states that it was in a dream that God appeared.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "(7) ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "In that night did God appear unto Solomon.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "—Kings, “In Gibeon did Jehovah appear unto Solomon in a dream of the night.” Our text fixes the night as that which followed the sacrifices; the parallel passage explicitly states that it was in a dream that God appeared.",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Ask what I shall give thee.—Rather, Ash thou! what shall I give thee? So Kings.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "Ask what I shall give thee.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "—Rather, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": "Ash thou! what shall I give thee?",
            "children": []
          },
          {
